    "https://schema.org/text": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\t\n\n\n7:00PM, Thursday, August 6, 2026\nRemai Modern – SaskTel Theatre\n\n\n102 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 0L3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nThe Best of Season 95\n\n\n7:00PM, Thursday, August 13, 2026\nRemai Modern – SaskTel Theatre\n\n\n102 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 0L3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nEverything is Romantic\n\n\n7:00PM, Thursday, August 20, 2026\nRemai Modern – SaskTel Theatre\n\n\n102 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 0L3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nA Change is Gonna Come\n\n\n7:00PM, Thursday, August 27, 2026\nRemai Modern – SaskTel Theatre\n\n\n102 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 0L3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nThe Traveller\n\n\n\nStep away from the heat this summer and into the air-conditioned Sasktel Theatre at Remai Modern for FREE community screenings of your Saskatoon Symphony Orchestra!\nWe are featuring four screenings, one every Thursday in August at 7:00PM. They all feature one of our favourite moments of our most recent season.\nIn our 95th season, we featured everything from local talent to global stars, showcasing the SSO at its best. The concert films featured in this partnership with Remai Modern are just a few of the 65+ available at http://ConcertStream.tv, where you can also find behind the scenes, interviews, and more!\nWatch our concerts for free every Thursday in August at the Remai Modern Sasktel Theatre at 7:00PM.\nAugust 6 – Best of Season 95\nAugust 13 – Everything is Romantic\nAugust 20 – A Change is Gonna Come\nAugust 27 – The Traveller\n\n\n\t\t"
      }
    ]
  },
