      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\t\n\n\n10:00AM, Friday, January 29, 2027\nNutrien Wonderhub\n\n\n950 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H6\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nRegister\n\n\n11:15AM, Friday, January 29, 2027\nNutrien Wonderhub\n\n\n950 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H6\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nRegister\n\n\n10:00AM, Saturday, January 30, 2027\nNutrien Wonderhub\n\n\n950 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H6\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nRegister\n\n\n11:15AM, Saturday, January 30, 2027\nNutrien Wonderhub\n\n\n950 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H6\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nRegister\n\n\n\nWe are blasting off into space! Climb aboard the Saskatoon Symphony’s rocket ship and head out into the stars. Who will we meet? What will we do? And what stories will we have when we return home? Join us for an out of this world musical adventure!\nSpecifically designed for your mini-maestro, these parent and child experiences are perfect for your 2- to 4-year-old music lover.\nExplore music through movement, song and dance with SSO musicians. Let the music connect you and your child and send you both on a journey through melody, rhythm, colour, and beautiful sound.\n\n\n\t\t"
      }
    ]
  },
