    "https://schema.org/text": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\t\n\n\n10:00AM, Thursday, April 8, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Friday, April 9, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Saturday, April 10, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Sunday, April 11, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Thursday, April 15, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Friday, April 16, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Saturday, April 17, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Sunday, April 18, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Thursday, April 22, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Friday, April 23, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Saturday, April 24, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n10:00AM, Sunday, April 25, 2027\nSaskatoon Symphony Orchestra\n\n\n602 B 51st Street\nSaskatoon, Saskatchewan S7K 7K3\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nFind Out More\n\n\n\nIt’s time for another Book & Music Sale! The spring sale is Thursdays through Sundays from April 8 to April 25 in the warehouse at 602B 51st Street E (entrance at the back). Sale hours are 10 am – 6 pm each day.\nWe sell all kinds of reading, listening & viewing media!\nAll formats of books and music are sold, including:\n\nBooks: hardcover, softcover, trade, paperback, textbooks, booklets, sets, new, used, large print, signed by author\nMusic sheets and songbooks\nMusic: CDs, vinyl records (LPs, EPs, 33-1/3 rpm, 45 rpm, 78 rpm, even 16-2/3 rpm spoken word records), prerecorded cassette and 8-track tapes, sets, sealed, unsealed, coloured vinyl\nVideos: DVDs, prerecorded VHS and Beta cassette tapes, sets\n\nHow to find the Book & Music Sale:\n602B 51st Street E\n(Back Entrance)\nSaskatoon, SK\nClick here for more information about the Book & Music Sale.\n\n\n\t\t"
      }
    ]
  },
