    "https://schema.org/text": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\n\t\t\t\n\n\n10:00AM, Friday, May 14, 2027\nNutrien Wonderhub\n\n\n950 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H6\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nRegister\n\n\n11:15AM, Friday, May 14, 2027\nNutrien Wonderhub\n\n\n950 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H6\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nRegister\n\n\n10:00AM, Saturday, May 15, 2027\nNutrien Wonderhub\n\n\n950 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H6\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nRegister\n\n\n11:15AM, Saturday, May 15, 2027\nNutrien Wonderhub\n\n\n950 Spadina Crescent E\nSaskatoon, SK S7K 3H6\nGoogle Maps Directions\n\n\nRegister\n\n\n\nARRRRR mateys, ahoy! Thar be treasure in that thar symphony…Come along with the Saskatoon Symphony on a pirate adventure in search of buried treasure. We need your help to follow the map and find the pirate chest!\nSpecifically designed for your mini-maestro, these parent and child experiences are perfect for your 2- to 4-year-old music lover.\nExplore music through movement, song and dance with SSO musicians. Let the music connect you and your child and send you both on a journey through melody, rhythm, colour, and beautiful sound.\n\n\n\t\t"
      }
    ]
  }
]
